{"chunk": "Bestyrelse og direktion har dags dato behandlet og
godkendt årsrapporten for 1. juli 2021 - 30. juni 2022 for
Bruhn Newtech A/S.
The Board of Directors and Board of Executives have
today discussed and approved the annual report for the
financial year 1 July 2021 - 30 June 2022 of Bruhn
Newtech A/S.", "context": "This chunk is the statement by management on the annual report of Bruhn Newtech A/S for the financial year 1 July 2021 - 30 June 2022."}
